title: PCA11_localized prostate cancer
source_name_ch1: human prostate cancer of untreated patient
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA with subsequent purification via RNeasy Columns
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the RiboAmp OA RNA 2 round amplification kit (Arcturus) starting from 1 ug RNA
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 microg of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip Drosophila Genome Array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Hewlett-Packard GeneArray Scanner G2500A.
description: Gene expression data from human prostate tissue with 90 percent tumor content
data_processing: The data were analyzed with the RMA algorithm in R using the quantile neromalization method
